item.title: CVE-2023-0360|2024-08-02T05:10:55.556Z -- unknown -- location%20weather
item.description: The Location Weather WordPress plugin before 1.3.4 does not validate and escape some of its block options before outputting them back in a page/post where the block is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
